{
  "stem": "214.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And for the first-- it's funny that we don't even remember-- it must have been maybe for about six months, there was no ghetto in Skierniewice.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was another thing which was really funny in a way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had this one-room apartment which my aunt found for us before.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was sort of cozy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know how big it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember the first Passovers there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was scrubbed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We all learned how to scrub the floors and the table-- you know the wooden table at home because tables are cheap in Poland because of the Polish, you know, peasant girl would come, and you didn't have to be a rich person to have-- to have a so-called maid, you know.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, and it sort of-- and I remember I even felt that it was sort of an adventure in a way.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and we lived across the street from the what you call [NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A base-- an army base, the Polish army base which was taken over by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And every so often, because we lived with those peasants, or those others that they had to come to this-- get whatever they needed from the-- the Germans, some permits for this or for that.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so off-- and I was out of school and I really spoke German as my foreign language and I spoke it really quite-- quite well.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So every so often, somebody would-- some Polish peasant would knock at the door and he'd say, do you speak any German?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And foolishly, I said would say, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would, well, can you help me because, you know, he didn't know any German and whoever the German soldier was, they couldn't communicate.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
